snippet.title: Zarvot - Teaser Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Zarvot is a game about cubes. Follow the adventures of Charcoal and as they attempt to make the ultimate birthday present for their best friend! And in Versus Mode, play against your friends in destructive, cutthroat cube action! Zarvot is launching first on Nintendo Switch in October 2018.

#NinetndoSwitch #Zarvot
